                                            <p>Need more things to think about. Ask us <a>here.</a> [ Join our community,
                                                meet our seniors, and ask questions that you have while practicing your
                                                english]</p>
                                            <p>TOEFL 7.0 | IELTS 6.5</p>
                                            <span>
                                                <p class="ep">Upload your file here: &#40;in <b
                                                        style="color: black;">.pdf</b> format&#41;</p>
                                                <input type="file" id="englishProficiency" name="englishproficiency"
                                                       accept=".pdf" required="">
                                            </span>
                                            <br><br><br>
                                            <div class="break">
                                                <button onclick="previousSlide();return false;">Previous</button>
                                                <input type="submit" value="Next" onclick="validateAccomplishmentsOne(); return false;">
